<h2 class="bold font-l">Stayin' Cool</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Mickey, Donald and Goofy try to beat an intense heatwave. </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="6r83rb" data-video-descrip="A heatwave strikes Big City, which the Greens suffer from." data-video-title="Heat Beaters" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/6r83rb_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/6r83rb.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/HeatWave" data-video-tropename="Heat Wave" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="WesternAnimation/BigCityGreens" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/6r83rb.jpg">
